"{\"uid\": \"variety.com-2024-digital-news-google-controversial-dear-sydney-gemini-ai-ad-pulled-nbc-olympics-1236094028\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  ByTodd Spangler  NY Digital Editor  Googlehas yanked an ad from NBC's Olympics broadcasts meant to highlight the power of itsGemini AItool - but which critics blasted as bizarrely tone-deaf.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999895744622, \"rank\": 9.537294717203776e-09, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 60-second ad, \\\"Dear Sydney,\\\" a father wants to help his daughter write a letter to her idol, Olympic track star Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999907061310168, \"rank\": 8.853388824487191e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a voiceover, the dad says his daughter \\\"might even be the world's No.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 Sydney fan.\\\"\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999907061310168, \"rank\": 8.853388824487191e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(According to Google, the father and daughter are real-life people.)\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9994895904455828, \"rank\": 0.0004952116766453347, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, in a jarring turn of events, he asks Google's Gemini AI to \\\"help my daughter write a letter telling Sydney how inspiring she is and be sure to mention that my daughter plans on breaking her world record one day.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9994895904455828, \"rank\": 0.0004952116766453347, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9995308496547646, \"rank\": 0.0004693705505511099, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.993452123899206, \"rank\": 0.006591033051776018, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999907061310168, \"rank\": 8.853388824487191e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She says sorry, not sorry.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \")\\\"Related Stories'Wicked: For Good' Director Jon M. Chu Says Ariana Grande and C